# MCP server test fixtures. The `.in.json` / `.assert.json` pairs are static
# JSON-RPC payloads, and `data/*.maxon` files are inputs piped at the fmt /
# run_program tools — none of them belong to the test-runner compilation unit.
# Without this flag, `maxon build maxon-dev-mcp/test` would try to compile the
# `data/*.maxon` fixtures (each defining its own `main`) and fail with
# duplicate-symbol errors.
